00:33:31.000 --> 00:33:39.220
<v C06D3439-3D87-4C31-96F6-8AFF5C235318>Al: Like if, like, seriously, like if you, if you disagree with any animal consumption, full stop, right?

748
00:33:31.819 --> 00:33:33.859
<v 8C4BDD3A-4510-4A99-8C76-F1B70ABE3F65>Kevin: Yeah.

749
00:33:38.000 --> 00:33:38.502
<v 8C4BDD3A-4510-4A99-8C76-F1B70ABE3F65>Kevin: Mm-hmm.

750
00:33:39.220 --> 00:33:44.079
<v C06D3439-3D87-4C31-96F6-8AFF5C235318>Al: Which I personally do not, but I am not going to say that someone is wrong for believing that.

751
00:33:44.079 --> 00:33:55.119
<v C06D3439-3D87-4C31-96F6-8AFF5C235318>Al: If that is what your opinion is, I don't see how hooking a fish on a hook and then throwing it into a fish tank is somehow better.

752
